{%- comment -%}
  Smart collection URL resolver.

  Usage:
    <a href="{% render 'collection-url', handle: 'womens-water-shoes' %}">…</a>

  Resolution order:
    1. If a collection with this handle exists → /collections/<handle>
    2. Otherwise → /collections/all/<handle>
       (Shopify natively filters /collections/all by a single product tag
        when the URL has the form /collections/all/<tag>. So as long as the
        product is tagged with this handle, the link works — no need to
        create a collection in admin.)
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if collections[handle].id != blank -%}/collections/{{ handle }}{%- else -%}/collections/all/{{ handle }}{%- endif -%}
